import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { Router } from '@angular/router'; import { NewUser } from 'src/app/interface/newUser'; import { AuthServicio } from 'src/app/servicios/auth.service'; import { ClientEntity } from 'src/app/interface/clientEntity'; @Component({ selector: 'app-registro', templateUrl: './registro.component.html', styleUrls: ['./registro.component.css'] }) export class RegistroComponent { constructor(private _router: Router, private _service: AuthServicio){} public newUser: NewUser = { email: '', password: '', passwordconfirm: '', firstName: '', surname: '', lastName: '', surLastName: '', docType:0, docNumber: '', country:0, phoneNumber: '', phoneType:0 }; clienteCreado?: ClientEntity; onregistry(){ this._service.Login(this.newUser) .subscribe((respuesta: ClientEntity) => { console.log(respuesta); this._router.navigate(['Tienda/home']); }).add(() => { }); } }
